      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated inline-six mated to a crisp six-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity and benefits from a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains tight, with bushings and dampers providing a communicative feedback loop through the hydraulic steering rack. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and valve adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all cylinders and VANOS timing\u2014are within tight tolerances. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
